<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得马上赶到阳光咖啡厅。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“僵尸们正在害人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西回到位子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚想起来了。我……嗯…….要去给潘校长帮忙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速跑过走廊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开门，飞上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们站在阳光咖啡厅外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走近了才发现，他们不是普通人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的眼神空洞。他们的头发很乱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们行走的方式很奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“僵尸！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人站在阳光咖啡厅的门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正拿着扫帚赶僵尸们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>僵尸们的大嘴巴一张一合的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走开！”女人吼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向下飞，推开了门前的僵尸们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跟女人跑进了屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人锁上了身后的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”女人用手擦了一下额头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是太可怕了！幸好你来了，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事儿。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她看到了史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站在一个柜子旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>柜子里只剩下几个甜甜圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的头发很乱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西大声喊道，“还有一个僵尸！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很有意思，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用手整理了一下头发。“我早上忘了梳头了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西指着窗外问。“是什么让那些人都变成了僵尸？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挠挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的头发更乱了。“我不太清楚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人指着柜子说。“是那些甜甜圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道的？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才来了一个男人。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他吃了一个甜甜圈以后变得很不正常。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想要咬其他客人，被我赶了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来又有别的人吃了甜甜圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们身上也发生了同样事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探打开柜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出一个甜甜圈研究起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得跟普通的甜甜圈一样啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这种事情以前发生过吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人摇摇头。“一次也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我刚刚从一家新面包厂订了这些甜甜圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是我收到的第一批。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这家面包厂叫什么名字？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“勒·斯威特面包厂。”女人说，“就在城外，山旁边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去那里看看。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑出咖啡厅，飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沿着街区，罗西看到乐购超市的门突然打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一大群僵尸从门里涌了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>